# Development env — loaded automatically by Expo for `expo start`.
# Vars must be prefixed EXPO_PUBLIC_ to be readable in the app (Expo inlines them).
#
# Left UNSET on purpose: api.ts auto-detects your Mac's LAN host (Expo hostUri),
# which reaches the dev server from a physical device AND the simulator.
# Uncomment to force a host instead:
#   iOS simulator        -> http://localhost:8080
#   Android emulator     -> http://10.0.2.2:8080
#   physical device      -> http://<your-mac-LAN-IP>:8080
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8080
